      • maximalSubgraphs

        public void maximalSubgraphs()
                      throws lpsolve.LpSolveException
        We want that two nodes are mapped if they have the most mapped subgraphs, i.e. if we have a node n which can be mapped onto nodes u and v, then we want that n is mapped onto the node with which n's subgraph has the most in common.
        Throws:
        lpsolve.LpSolveException
